# Example pynote env file. The REAL one lives at ~/.pynote/.env (preferred)
# or is set via a shell `export`. Do NOT put a real key in this repo — .env
# is gitignored and excluded from sdist, but keeping secrets out of the
# source tree at all is the safer default.

ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Optional:
# PYNOTE_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-6
# PYNOTE_MAX_TOKENS=4096
